VALUES ('B2_U13_B2_I1', 'ingles-b2-U13', 6, 'multiple_choice_cloze', 'Complete the sentences with the correct word from the options provided.', '{"prompt_es":"Complete the sentences with the correct word from the options provided.","mastery_tag":"vocabulary:b2-lifestyle","main_text":"In today’s fast-paced world, maintaining a balanced (1)[GAP 1] is essential for our mental and physical health. Many people are now focusing on their (2)[GAP 2] by incorporating healthy meals and regular exercise into their routines. Moreover, personal (3)[GAP 3] is becoming increasingly important as individuals strive to improve their skills and knowledge. Mindfulness practices, such as meditation, can greatly enhance our overall (4)[GAP 4] and help us manage stress effectively. Ultimately, a positive (5)[GAP 5] can lead to a more fulfilled and satisfying life.","gaps":[{"id":"1","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"lifestyle"},{"id":"o2","text":"duty"},{"id":"o3","text":"task"},{"id":"o4","text":"hobby"}]},{"id":"2","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"well-being"},{"id":"o2","text":"safety"},{"id":"o3","text":"wealth"},{"id":"o4","text":"knowledge"}]},{"id":"3","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"growth"},{"id":"o2","text":"decline"},{"id":"o3","text":"stagnation"},{"id":"o4","text":"routine"}]},{"id":"4","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"health"},{"id":"o2","text":"environment"},{"id":"o3","text":"economy"},{"id":"o4","text":"performance"}]},{"id":"5","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"mindset"},{"id":"o2","text":"feedback"},{"id":"o3","text":"structure"},{"id":"o4","text":"schedule"}]}],"correct_answer":{"1":"o1","2":"o1","3":"o1","4":"o1","5":"o1"},"explanation":"(1) El estilo de vida se refiere a la forma en que vive una persona, incluyendo sus hábitos y rutinas diarias.\n(2) El bienestar se refiere al estado de sentirse saludable y feliz, tanto física como mentalmente.\n(3) El crecimiento personal implica el desarrollo y la mejora de habilidades y cualidades a lo largo del tiempo.\n(4) La salud es un factor clave en el bienestar general y afecta cómo nos sentimos y cómo funcionamos en la vida diaria.\n(5) La mentalidad se refiere a las creencias y actitudes que influyen en cómo las personas ven el mundo y abordan la vida.","complexity":3,"concept_tags":["vocabulary","lifestyle","unit","grammar"]}')
