VALUES ('B2_U14_B2_I1', 'ingles-b2-U14', 6, 'fill_blanks', 'Fill in the blanks with the correct words.', '{"prompt_es":"Fill in the blanks with the correct words.","mastery_tag":"reading:b2-complex-texts","main_text":"In today’s world, the ability to analyze complex texts is more important than ever. Many people find it challenging to (1)___ the arguments presented in various media. Often, these texts require a detailed (2)___ of the author''s intent and the context in which they were written. Additionally, the use of persuasive techniques can (3)___ the reader’s judgment. To fully grasp the material, one must approach it with a critical (4)___, questioning the validity of the claims made. Furthermore, understanding (5)___ distinctions between various viewpoints can enhance one’s ability to engage in constructive discussions.","correct_answer":["interpret","analysis","cloud","mindset","nuanced"],"explanation":"(1) Interpretar significa entender o aclarar el significado de algo.\n(2) Análisis es el proceso de examinar algo en detalle.\n(3) Nublar significa dificultar la claridad o comprensión de un tema.\n(4) Mentalidad se refiere a la forma de pensar que uno tiene.\n(5) Matizado significa tener sutiles diferencias o variaciones.","complexity":3,"concept_tags":["reading","complex","texts","unit"]}')
