VALUES ('B2_U15_B3_I5', 'ingles-b2-U15', 7, 'multiple_choice', 'What outcome is achieved by effectively articulating complex arguments?', '{"prompt_es":"What outcome is achieved by effectively articulating complex arguments?","mastery_tag":"reading:b2-complex-texts","explanation":"Articular argumentos complejos de manera efectiva ayuda a obtener el apoyo necesario para las iniciativas, lo que mejora los resultados comerciales.","stimulus_en":"In today''s competitive business environment, understanding complex arguments is vital for success. Many companies face challenges when trying to adapt to rapid changes in consumer behavior and technology. An effective approach to this problem involves analyzing market trends and employing strategic thinking. Companies must understand not only their own strengths and weaknesses but also those of their competitors. This knowledge allows businesses to position themselves advantageously in the market. Furthermore, clear communication of these analyses to stakeholders is crucial for aligning interests and driving the business forward. As a result, leaders who can articulate complex arguments effectively are often more successful in securing buy-in for their initiatives, ultimately leading to better business outcomes.","correct_answer":"o1","options":[{"id":"o1","text":"Securing buy-in for initiatives."},{"id":"o2","text":"Understanding complex arguments"},{"id":"o3","text":"To adapt to rapid changes."},{"id":"o4","text":"By understanding their strengths and weaknesses."}],"complexity":3,"concept_tags":["reading","complex","texts","unit","grammar"]}')
